<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Application Confirmation - IECA</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a 0%, #1e293b 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 120px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .confirmation-box {
            background: #f0f9ff;
            border: 2px solid #3b82f6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .application-id {
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1d4ed8;
            background: white;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        .timeline {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .timeline h3 {
            color: #0f172a;
            margin-top: 0;
        }
        .step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 15px 0;
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .step-number {
            background: #3b82f6;
            color: white;
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-right: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            padding: 20px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="cid:ieca-logo" alt="IECA Logo" class="logo">
            <h1>üìù Application Received</h1>
            <p>Indian Error Cyber Army - Membership Application</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
            
            <p>
                Thank you for applying to join the <strong>Indian Error Cyber Army</strong>! We have successfully received your membership application and are excited to review your submission.
            </p>
            
            <div class="confirmation-box">
                <h3>‚úÖ Application Confirmed</h3>
                <p>Your application ID:</p>
                <div class="application-id">{{applicationId}}</div>
                <p><small>Please keep this ID for your records</small></p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="timeline">
                <h3>üìã What Happens Next:</h3>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">1</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Application Review</strong><br>
                        Our team will review your application and credentials (2-3 business days)
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">2</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Background Verification</strong><br>
                        We'll verify your cybersecurity experience and commitment to ethical practices
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">3</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Decision Notification</strong><br>
                        You'll receive an email with our decision and next steps
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-number">4</div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Welcome & Onboarding</strong><br>
                        If approved, you'll get access to all IECA resources and community features
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                <strong>Application Status:</strong> Under Review<br>
                <strong>Expected Response:</strong> Within 3-5 business days<br>
                <strong>Support Contact:</strong> applications@ieca.zehrasec.com
            </p>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 30px;">
                We appreciate your interest in joining India's premier cybersecurity community. Our rigorous selection process ensures we maintain the highest standards of excellence and ethical commitment.
            </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <strong>Indian Error Cyber Army (IECA)</strong><br>
                Building India's Cybersecurity Future
            </p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px;">
                This is an automated confirmation email. Please do not reply to this message.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
